#: templates/emails/welcome_email.html:20 templates/emails/welcome_email.txt:4
msgid "Welcome to VoctEnsemble"
msgstr "Bienvenue chez VoctEnsemble"

#: templates/emails/welcome_email.html:26
msgid "Your stage awaits"
msgstr "Votre scène vous attend"

#: templates/emails/welcome_email.html:54 templates/emails/welcome_email.txt:7
msgid ""
"We are thrilled to welcome you to VoctManager — the digital heart of our "
"artistic operations. This platform was designed to streamline our creative "
"process, from repertoire management to concert logistics, ensuring you can "
"focus entirely on the music."
msgstr ""
"Nous sommes ravis de vous accueillir sur VoctManager — le cœur numérique de "
"nos opérations artistiques. Cette plateforme a été conçue pour fluidifier "
"notre processus créatif, de la gestion du répertoire à la logistique "
"concertante, afin que vous puissiez vous concentrer entièrement sur la "
"musique."

#: templates/emails/welcome_email.html:64
msgid ""
"Your profile has been provisioned and is ready to explore. Should you "
"encounter any difficulty accessing your account, our administration team "
"remains at hand."
msgstr ""
"Votre profil a été provisionné et est prêt à être exploré. Si vous "
"rencontrez la moindre difficulté pour accéder à votre compte, notre équipe "
"d'administration reste à votre disposition."

#: templates/emails/welcome_email.html:74
msgid "All that remains is to take your place."
msgstr "Il ne vous reste plus qu'à prendre votre place."

#: templates/emails/welcome_email.html:89
msgid "Projects &amp; Repertoire"
msgstr "Projets &amp; Répertoire"

#: templates/emails/welcome_email.html:93
#: templates/emails/welcome_email.txt:20
msgid ""
"View your upcoming projects, concert programmes, and casting assignments."
msgstr ""
"Consultez vos projets à venir, les programmes de concerts et les "
"distributions."

#: templates/emails/welcome_email.html:106
#: templates/emails/welcome_email.txt:22
msgid "Sheet Music"
msgstr "Partitions"

#: templates/emails/welcome_email.html:110
#: templates/emails/welcome_email.txt:23
msgid ""
"Access your digital score library — scores and audio materials, organised by"
" project."
msgstr ""
"Accédez à votre bibliothèque numérique — partitions et enregistrements "
"audio, organisés par projet."

#: templates/emails/welcome_email.html:123
#: templates/emails/welcome_email.txt:25
msgid "Rehearsal Schedule"
msgstr "Calendrier des répétitions"

#: templates/emails/welcome_email.html:127
#: templates/emails/welcome_email.txt:26
msgid ""
"Stay up to date with rehearsal times, locations, and any last-minute "
"changes."
msgstr ""
"Restez informé des horaires de répétitions, des lieux et de toute "
"modification de dernière minute."

#: templates/emails/welcome_email.html:146
msgid "Your personal workspace"
msgstr "Votre espace de travail personnel"

#: templates/emails/welcome_email.html:154
msgid "Access Your Dashboard"
msgstr "Accéder à mon tableau de bord"

#: templates/emails/welcome_email.html:159
